Class TimestampCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.data.DataCell
      • org.knime.core.data.def.TimestampCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, DataValue, TimestampValue
    Deprecated. 
    Date and time in KNIME is represented by DateAndTimeValue and DateAndTimeCell. This class will be removed in future versions of KNIME.

    @Deprecated
public class TimestampCell
extends DataCell
implements TimestampValue
